<h2 id="题目1">题目1：</h2>
<p>这题先尝试了一下CRT，结果发现逆元不存在，就想到了不互素的解法，在xenny的工坊学过，但是也没完全理解，直接用了脚本</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">from Crypto.Util.number import *
from gmpy2 import *
nl = [,,]
cl = [,,]

def excrt(m, r):
   lcm = m[0]
   R = r[0]
   for i in range(1, len(m)):
       d, x, y = gcdext(lcm, m[i])
       c = R - r[i]
       if c % d:
           return -1
       x = x * c // d % (m[i] // d)
       R -= lcm * x
       lcm = lcm * m[i] // d
       R %= lcm
   return (R + lcm) % lcm

m = excrt(nl, cl)
for i in range (10,20):
   print(m.bit_length()//i)
   print(long_to_bytes(iroot(m, i)[0]))
#flag{326177d1-448f-48a6-abdd-ee2085b28eaf} 
</code></pre>
